    "# IDRS PART 7: Full Ensemble Pipeline · Final Evaluation · Resilience Testing\n",
    "## Educational Web Platform Intrusion Detection & Automated Response System\n",
    "\n",
    "**This is the final integration notebook — depends on all previous parts.**\n",
    "\n",
    "**Scope of Part 7:**\n",
    "- End-to-end inference pipeline: raw input → ensemble decision → response\n",
    "- Soft-voting ensemble: RF + XGB + LGBM + CNN-LSTM + Autoencoder + DistilBERT\n",
    "- Final benchmark table across ALL models and ALL threat types\n",
    "- Adversarial robustness test (feature noise injection + payload obfuscation)\n",
    "- Concept drift simulation over a long traffic stream\n",
    "- Per-threat-class detection rate analysis\n",
    "- False positive analysis (critical: avoid blocking legitimate students)\n",
    "- Response time distribution across threat tiers\n",
    "- Executive summary with publication-quality figures\n",
    "- Full serialised pipeline (joblib) ready for deployment"
   ]
